    " You can then assign it directly inside your VALUE expression:
    DATA(lv_local_changed_at) = lv_current_timestamp.
* read decision comment-------------------

*--- read the workitem container to access the decision note
    CALL FUNCTION 'SAP_WAPI_READ_CONTAINER'
      EXPORTING
        workitem_id      = iv_workitemid
      IMPORTING
        return_code      = lv_return_code
